com.arangodb.async

Interface ArangoRouteAsync

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArangoSerializationAccessor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArangoRouteAsyncImpl

    public interface ArangoRouteAsync
extends ArangoSerializationAccessor
    Interface for a specific path to be used to perform arbitrary requests.
    Author:
    Mark Vollmary
